!     PURPOSE--PRINT THE OUTPUT FOR THE PPCC TEST
!              (UNCENSORED, UNGROUPED CASE) IN ASCII, HTML, LATEX,
!              OR RTF FORMAT
!     WRITTEN BY--ALAN HECKERT
